This paper is about generating high-resolution, photo-realistic images using machine learning techniques. The paper discusses a method for synthesizing novel images by performing gradient ascent in the latent space of a generator network. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
